  "description": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"OnTheGo Platforms is bringing gesture recognition to Google Glass apps (video)\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/e721629041a8749f14e1b10ea8383f87/on-the-go-pltforms-lede.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div><br />\n<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/googleglass\">Google Glass</a> 应付语音和触控有一套，但到目前为止，其应用并不支持手势操作。为了解决这个问题，来自美国波特兰的 OnTheGo Platforms 团队专门开发了一套 SDK，希望其它开发者能把手势辨识加入到他们的 Glass 应用中去（或者是基于 Android 系统的眼镜，比如 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/01/07/vuzix-smart-glasses-m100/\">Vuzix M100</a>）。在 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/ces2014\">CES</a> 现场我们动手玩了一下他们迄今为止的成果，想看视频和更多感想的话就点击继续阅读吧。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/onthego-platforms-google-glass-gesture-recognition-at-ces/\">OnTheGo Platforms Google Glass gesture recognition at CES</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/onthego-platforms-google-glass-gesture-recognition-at-ces/6434215/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/screenshot-2014-01-08-10-34-27-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/onthego-platforms-google-glass-gesture-recognition-at-ces/6434216/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/screenshot-2014-01-08-10-35-21-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/onthego-platforms-google-glass-gesture-recognition-at-ces/6434217/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/screenshot-2014-01-08-10-35-31-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div></div><p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/09/onthego-platforms-google-glass-gesture-recognition-controls/\" rel=\"bookmark\">继续阅读全文 <em>OnTheGo Platforms 为 Google Glass 应用带来手势辨识功能（视频）</em></a></p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a 